36 Fur Coat 9 Halves the damage from physical moves.
54 Thermal Exchange 6 Boosts the Attack stat when hit by a Fire-type move. The Pokémon also cannot be burned.
72 Bare Hands 6 Boosts the base power of the Pokémon's attacks if they are not holding an item.

By Disc

Disc Ability Score Description
Disc 02 Pickup 2 The Pokémon may pick up the items, both during and outside of battle.
Disc 10 Water Veil 4 The Pokémon is covered with a water veil, which prevents the Pokémon from getting a burn.
Disc 11 Ball Fetch 1 If the Pokémon is not holding an item, it will fetch the first failed thrown Poké Ball.
Disc 12 Sturdy 7 It cannot be knocked out with one hit. One-hit KO moves cannot knock it out, either.
Disc 18 Mimicry 3 Changes the Pokémon's type depending on the terrain.
Disc 28 Snow Warning 9 The Pokémon summons a hailstorm when it enters a battle.
Disc 41 Swift Swim 6 Boosts the Pokémon's Speed stat in rain.
Disc 46 Fog Veil 6 Boosts the Pokémon's evasiveness in thick fog.
Disc 52 Damp 2 Prevents the use of explosive moves, such as Self-Destruct, by dampening its surroundings.
